OL,3,CWoman admits manslaughter of her
OL,4,Cgrandmother
OL,6,FA woman has admitted to the
OL,7,Fmanslaughter of a 93-year-old great-
OL,8,Fgrandmother on the grounds of
OL,9,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,11,FJudy Zussman was found dead at a
OL,12,Fproperty on Altrincham Road, in
OL,13,FGatley, Stockport, on 16 April 2024.
OL,15,FHer granddaughter, Amelia Ali, 40, was
OL,16,Finitially charged with her murder but
OL,17,Fat a plea hearing on Tuesday 13
OL,18,FJanuary, Ali pleaded guilty to the
OL,19,Falternative charge of manslaughter on
OL,20,Fthe grounds of diminished
OL,21,Fresponsibility.
