OL,3,CWoman admits manslaughter of her
OL,4,Cgrandmother
OL,6,FThe court was told that the three
OL,7,Fexperts in the case who prepared
OL,8,Freports on Ali agreed that she was
OL,9,Fsuffering from "abnormal mental
OL,10,Ffunctioning arising from a recognised
OL,11,Fmental illness".
OL,13,FAs a result of the strength of the
OL,14,Fevidence from the experts, the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service accepted the plea
OL,16,Fto the lesser charge.
