OL,3,CWoman admits manslaughter of her
OL,4,Cgrandmother
OL,6,FMr Rhind KC said before the incident,
OL,7,FAli and Ms Zussman had a "close and
OL,8,Floving relationship" and that there
OL,9,Fwas no suggestion of any incidents of
OL,10,Fviolence previously. "On the night
OL,11,Fitself, she was taken to her
OL,12,Fgrandmother's house and things were
OL,13,Fcalm," he said.
OL,15,F"Simply, there is no explanation in
OL,16,Fwhy she would attack her grandmother
OL,17,Fso brutally, and it is felt it was her
OL,18,Fdelusional beliefs that her mother had
OL,19,Fharmed her children."
