OL,3,CWoman admits manslaughter of her
OL,4,Cgrandmother
OL,6,FNina Grahame KC, defending, added:
OL,7,F"What happened in this case, is that
OL,8,Ffor the first time she has had a clear
OL,9,Fdiagnosis of a severe mental illness
OL,10,Fincluding manic episodes.
OL,12,F"Her delusional state on the date of
OL,13,Fthese tragic events is her belief that
OL,14,Fher mother was harming her children
OL,15,Fand the misidentification of her
OL,16,Fgrandmother at the time. They were
OL,17,Fdelusions."
OL,19,FAli was remanded into custody and will
OL,20,Fnext appear for sentence on 12 March.
